                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 120.) I accompanied Horsnell on the 7th of Nov. to Newgate, and he pointed out Smith in the prisoner's pre<lb></lb>sence—I had Smith in my custody last Session. <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18421128-30-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
